This is a backend meant to be used with a SPA like react

Users can sign up, log in, post, reply, get posts, get replies

Run tests: ./tests/run_tests.sh
Start server: ./start_server.sh

Download the necessary packages:
>> virtualenv backend_flask_proj
>> source backend_flask_proj/scripts/activate
>> pip install -r requirements.txt

Please use postman to query the api, there is no frontend implementation at this point